HEADWORD: Micronesians
<hw>Mi`cro*ne"sians</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos>; <sing>sing.
<singw>Micronesian</singw></sing>. <fld>(Ethnol.)</fld> <def>A dark race
